      <title>日本石川地区发生 5.9 级地震</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-02/strong-earthquakes-shake-area-near-japanese-region-hit-by-jan-1-fatal-disaster-but-no-tsunami</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京（美联社）——周一凌晨地震再次袭击日本中北部地区石川，该地区仍未从 1 月 1 日强烈地震造成的破坏中恢复，但最新的震动并未造成重大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-02/strong-earthquakes-shake-area-near-japanese-region-hit-by-jan-1-fatal-disaster-but-no-tsunami</guid>
